Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,See? That's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes. Cat ears are your time, Fujiwara,\Nas to Shinomiya is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}the time you brought was originally\NShinomiya and cat ears alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cat ears and girls!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mutualism!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are relationships in this world\Nthat are naturally symbiotic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clovers and honeybees!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Crocodiles and hummingbirds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Avocados and soy sauce!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And cats...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cats, which a great majority\Nof humans love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And here we have Kaguya Shinomiya,\Na graceful girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}How will the compatibility\Nof those two things be reflected in him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}MIRACULOUS COMPATIBILITY (MARRIAGE)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A marriage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}KAGUYA WANTS AFFECTION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is it really necessary to cosplay\Nfor the welcome party?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an6}FRENCH EXCHANGE STUDENT\NWELCOME SCHEDULE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,France is the biggest cosplaying nation\Nright after Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,With cosplaying, you don't need words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's no better way\Nto overcome the language barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and deepen our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you think, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}MIRACULOUS COMPATIBILITY (MARRIAGE)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A marriage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Cute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not bad, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}No good! Whenever I look at Shinomiya,\Nmy face tenses up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I need to calm down and look normal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a scary look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not much of a reaction.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks like this kind of thing\Ndoesn't suit me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'd probably look better on someone\Nwith more charm, like Miss Fujiwara.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You wear a pair, too, President.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}MEOW
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How can I put it? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You don't hold back, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You knew beforehand\Nthat this wouldn't look good on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,True!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cuuute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}MIRACULOUS COMPATIBILITY (MARRIAGE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A marriage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? The president just has cat ears on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The reaction of others aside,\Nit was a perfect combo in Kaguya's mind!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}What should I do?\NI can't get my mouth to stop smiling!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll be obvious to him\Nthat I think he looks cute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since it's come to this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Skill... Biting one's tongue!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's not a perfect method.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}GRIN GRIN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A half-grin remained on her face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}SHIVER SHIVER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's the smirk for, Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is there something\Nyou'd like to say about my cat ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}GRIN GRIN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They look...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,very good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That expression!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}As if looking at a bug!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does it mean I look so terrible\Nthat I barely qualify as human?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miss Fujiwara,\Nlet's take a photo of the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We have to preserve this moment\Nfor future generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She means for extortion!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll put it away and use it\Nas a bargaining chip someday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Forget about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kaguya, you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shinomiya, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she takes my photo,\Nshe'll have me by the short hairs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}at the same time, I'll legally be able\Nto obtain a cute photo of her like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A balanced scale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}BALANCED SCALE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The weight of the merit\Nand demerit are the same!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you're going to take it,\Ndo it now, Fujiwara!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shirogane chooses the cute side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A side he would normally never choose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O-Oh. Take it with the 4K thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it! She's even cuter\Nwhen I'm standing right next to her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The muscles in my face are stiffening!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe that looks so good on him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! My mouth is smiling by itself again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C-Could both of you\Ngive me a cheerful smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- I can't!\N- I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I want to get closer to his cuteness!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to burn this image into my memory\Nfrom a shorter distance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you glaring at each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you're going to fight,\NI'm going to confiscate these!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}NAB
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel like I was possessed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Scary!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}CAT EARS ARE SCARY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Cat ears are scary!\N- Cat ears are scary!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH:\NFUJIWARA LOSES
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fujiwara loses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}HENCEFORTH, ALL MEMBERS\NOF STUDENT COUNCIL\NARE BANNED FROM WEARING CAT EARS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, the welcome party is next Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Other than making decorations, we need\Nto go shopping for souvenir sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}THE STUDENT COUNCIL\NWANTS IT TO BE SAID
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}We probably need two people for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}We'll need a few other things, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}and enough for all of the participants,\Nso that's a lot of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Which means giving up our day off\Nto go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Boy, what a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who'd wanna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'll be in trouble\Nif no one wants to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, if it's really necessary, I could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}FIDGET FIDGET
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why don't we play a game,\Nand the losers have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- A game?\N- A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes! The banned word game!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE BANNED WORD GAME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The banned word game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here's an example!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I write a word like this\Nand pass it to the person on my right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hold it up and don't look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}SIMPLE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's the word that person can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I get it. So you don't know\Nwhat your own banned word is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do it for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I pass it to the person on my right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should write a word\Nthat Fujiwara would be likely to say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the second and third place people\Nwill go shopping.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}FIRST PLACE DOESN'T GO\NSECOND AND THIRD PLACE GO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, a man is needed\Nfor the physical labor,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}STRONGER\N(THAN WOMEN)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}while no one knows more\Nabout traditional sweets than Shinomiya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}CERTIFIED TEA EXPERT\NKNOWLEDGEABLE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}It's just a matter of efficiency.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Therefore, I need to let Fujiwara win\Nwhile I beat Shinomiya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FIRST PLACE: FUJIWARA\NSECOND PLACE: ME\NTHIRD PLACE: SHINOMIYA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}CHECK-IT-OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure Fujiwara would never say this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll win for sure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}CHECK-IT-OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, are we ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yo, yo, let's get started, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fujiwara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When I play da banned word game,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,people always be choosin' words n' phrases\NI be sayin', but not now, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I be changin' da way I speak,\Nso my words be different, yo! Too bad, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't look at her!\NI don't want her to lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yo, yo, yo, yo, yo, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Crap, she'll end up saying, "check-it-out."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kaguya, what ya think your word is, yo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Say "Hooo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Say "Hooo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Say "Hooo"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's childish!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a surefire way to win this game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's by not talking at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Say "Yay!" Say "Yay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shinomiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Say "Yay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We won't get anywhere like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,At the bare minimum,\Nspeak enough to make it a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inevitable behavior.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}INEVITABLE BEHAVIOR
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}"That person would do this."\N"This person would say this."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This game produces a situation that draws\Nthe designated word out of your opponent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But how am I going to get her\Nto say that banned word?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My instinct is telling me, "You've spent\Nhalf a year trying to get her to say that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's impossible!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}But wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I can steer the conversation towards\Nsomething that Shinomiya loves doing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fujiwara,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,is there something you hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shirogane passed\Nthe word "hate" on to Fujiwara,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}a word that can easily\Nbe connected to "love."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What I hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:10:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,People often tell me I'm not good\Nat reading a situation, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But they also say that's a good thing, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But when they talk about love and stuff,\Nthey don't include me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They say I'd be sure\Nto step on a land mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's sound judgment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}When I think about making problems\Nfor people without even realizing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}it makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what I hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miss Fujiwara...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've never thought\Nyou've caused problems for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,there are many people who've been helped\Nby your straightforwardness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kaguya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You don't hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I mean... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're out, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an4}LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inevitable behavior!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}When all is said and done,\Nit was inevitable...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}that caring Kaguya would try\Nto comfort a depressed Fujiwara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fujiwara read that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was nasty!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Was all that a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.86,0:11:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It wasn't a lie, but a bluff, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course people would include me\Nin conversations about love interests, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Since we've gotten this far,\Nthe rest should be easy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'll lose automatically by letting\Nmy guard down and following her lead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}She's got everything she needs to win.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, when it rains, it pours, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}was that the truth?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}She said it was a bluff,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}but a bluff has power because\Nit's a pinch of a lie mixed with truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It must be nice, having no troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}If that's the case,\Nhow much of it was a lie?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Fujiwara was speaking\Nabout feeling alienated,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}were those words and her eyes all lies?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}If it's possible that they weren't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}then, I'm playing this game wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:12:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I can't stand the idea of hurting others\Nfor the sake of my own self-interest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}That's my credo,\Nand this situation relates to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Prioritizing my own circumstances\Nand purposely losing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}That would be self-interest\Nand truly alienate her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}The idea of going out shopping\Nwith Shinomiya may be appealing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I can't betray my own conviction!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fujiwara...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going to get serious here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're out, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes! I beat the president, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Inevitable behavior.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}An action a person would necessarily take\Ngiven certain circumstances.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,SERIOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}And predicting that\Nis the essential point of the game.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shopping, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, we lost,\Nso I guess we can't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The banned word game is a game that\Ndemands understanding of your opponents.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ah, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We're going to buy the souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH:\NUTTER DEFEAT FOR SHIROGANE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Results of today's match...\NUtter defeat for Shirogane.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right! I'm looking forward\Nto seeing what you get, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}THE HEART THROBBING\NSHOPPING ARC CONTINUES
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}CHECK-IT-OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Check-it-out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The president said we'd talk\Nabout shopping after he got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The day he bought a smartphone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,we exchanged e-mail addresses\Nand phone numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But I've been waiting and waiting,\Nand he still hasn't contacted me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}He has no intention\Nof sending me a message first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}"President, I'm looking forward\Nto tomorrow—"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, I thought\NI'd send a text on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't! I'm not sending the first text!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KAGUYA WANTS HIM TO SEND IT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}All this beating around the bush...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lady Kaguya, you're in love\Nwith President Shirogane, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have feelings for the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I'm only interested\Nbecause he's got the elements I lack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's definitely not love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:14:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, what if the secretary started\Ndating President Shirogane?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want the president\Nto take Miss Fujiwara away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Despite appearances,\Nshe's my dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}From: Fujiwara\NSubject: Octopus\NLook! A live octopus!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's your dear friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}If it weighs on your mind that much,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lady Kaguya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,instead of a text, why not call?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C-Call?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's expecting a text.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Exploit that carelessness,\Nand attack this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Carelessness? Attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's the perfect plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Before Lady Kaguya quibbles about it,\Nclick-click there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait! I'm not mentally prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SHIROGANE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}RINGING
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is Shinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Miyuki's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}U-Um, is the president...\NI mean, is Shirogane there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am Shirogane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I mean...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,i-is Miyuki there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, my son?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyuki! A girl's on the phone for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A girl's calling for him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wha... You don't answer\Nanother person's cell phone, Dad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's Shinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, Shinomiya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was calling about the plan for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is now okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm in the tub, but that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The tub?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then he's naked, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lady Kaguya, right now you're talking\Nto someone who's completely exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's muffled on your end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I'll call you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My phone is waterproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is a problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How about we meet tomorrow\Nat 11 am in front of Hachiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'll buy the sweets, then go to Hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}STRETCH OUT THE CONVERSATION MORE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I'll see you tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinomiya—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? What were you about to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}FROM: SHIROGANE\NI WAS TRYING TO TELL YOU SOMETHING\NAS YOU HUNG UP THE PHONE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.33,0:16:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}LOOKS LIKE TONIGHT WILL GET PRETTY COLD,\NSO BE WARM AND GO TO SLEEP\NGOOD NIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good for you. Your first text.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Results of today's match... Kaguya wins.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH:\NKAGUYA WINS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,THE NEXT DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It seems Shibuya Station is flooded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The president is waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no way he's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A text canceling our plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But it's the first text\NShinomiya has sent me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So I'll call that a win for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thankfully, my phone is waterproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}THE END OF THE HEART THROBBING\NSHOPPING ARC
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}TOOK 30 MINUTES\NTO SEND THE CANCELLATION TEXT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FRENCH FOREIGN EXCHANGE STUDENTS\NWELCOME PARTY
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We got it ready in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Headmaster, next time,\Nplease don't tell us so last-minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MIYUKI SHIROGANE WANTS TO TALK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, everyone, have a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you speak French, Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No. Not very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How about you, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I AM MIYUKI SHIROGANE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're not the president for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I just prepared by studying the handbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Liar!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can speak French?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My mom is a former diplomat,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so ever since I was little, she drummed\Nvarious languages into my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait a second.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Am I the only person here\Nwho can't speak French?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}COMPLETELY ISOLATED
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's completely isolated!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-Wh-What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they figure out\NI'm the only one who doesn't speak it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}President of student council\Nof a Japanese school can't speak French?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe he's just dumb.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HOW CUTE...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad, bad for my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shirogane...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}why do you think I suddenly asked you\Nto prepare a party?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must determine...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}whether you're truly someone\Nto whom this academy can be entrusted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real test begins now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Betsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}No need to go easy on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Make mincemeat out of Miyuki Shirogane\Nwith everything you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Betsy Beltoise, the vice-president\Nof the French school's student council.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her nickname is "The Wound-licking Razor."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}THE WOUND-LICKING RAZOR
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one has ever been impervious\Nto her verbal attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}VERBAL ATTACK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Betsy's sarcasm is like punching\Nsomeone you've just met in the face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next, she provokes him as if simultaneously\Ninsulting his parents and lover.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}On top of that,\Nshe diminishes his character{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}in a way that would make\Na man in his sixties break down in tears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}THAT'S IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyuki Shirogane!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He smiles confidently in the face\Nof that merciless verbal onslaught?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd be throwing up\Nwhile bowing down on the ground!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'd think he couldn't comprehend\Nwhat she was saying!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My verbal assault isn't getting through!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Betsy unleashes even stronger invective\Nagainst Shirogane.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, sorry.\NYou don't understand Japanese, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:21:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kaguya menaces Betsy with language that'd\Nget the attention of the Broadcasting Code.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shinomiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P-President!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea! That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She... She's going to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Japanese high school girls are scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, what did I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exhibition match. The Japanese school won.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}EXHIBITION MATCH\NTHE JAPANESE SCHOOL WON
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I bet you look down on me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After being so foul-mouthed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is like the old me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Like I said at the beginning,\NI skimmed the French handbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I couldn't have caught what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, I have no idea\Nwhat you were saying to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:22:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I just know you were mad\Nbecause she was badmouthing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's one thing I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.52,0:22:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, don't do that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It only makes me wanna know more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A secret is a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Results of today's match...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}RESULTS OF TODAY'S MATCH:\NBOTH WINNERS
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It wasn't in French.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Both winners.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- In Latin?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5}BECAUSE THEY SHOWED\NEACH OTHER THEIR WEAKNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- In Yiddish?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- In Finnish?\N- No.
